WEBVTT

00:00.313 --> 00:01.982
Uncle Scrooge!
You're sick,

00:02.025 --> 00:03.026
you shouldn't be on your feet.

00:03.113 --> 00:04.580
I have to make
my morning meeting.

00:04.668 --> 00:06.812
A stuffy nose and
clogged ears won't kill me.

00:06.900 --> 00:09.359
Yeah, he's vanquished
mythical beasts,

00:09.447 --> 00:12.119
demonic armies,
robot uprisings!

00:12.221 --> 00:13.697
Which would probably
wear out

00:13.785 --> 00:16.123
someone half his
advanced age.

00:16.212 --> 00:17.954
Advanced age?!

00:21.619 --> 00:24.923
For the last time, I'm not sick!

00:31.923 --> 00:33.633
According to the
Junior Woodchuck Guidebook,

00:33.720 --> 00:35.014
your
sickness could be...

00:35.587 --> 00:36.634
Finally.

00:36.721 --> 00:40.611
A quick dip before my meeting
is all I need to vim my vigor.

00:44.285 --> 00:45.767
Ahh!

00:51.892 --> 00:54.361
I've been robbed!

